DOC.brief_summary: To evaluate effect feed infant formula contain L. paracasei ssp . paracasei strain F19 Whey Protein Concentrate .
DOC.brief_title: Feeding Infant Formula With Added Probiotics Whey Protein Concentrate
DOC.criteria: Inclusion criterion ( formulafed group ) : healthy infant mother could voluntarily resign completely breastfeed infant age 14 plus/minus 3 day Inclusion criterion ( breastfed group ) : healthy infant exclusively breastfed birth mother intend breastfeed > 80 % least 5th month age ( mean 4th month age ) . Inclusion criterion ( infant ) : deliver 37 42 week gestation birth weight > 2500 g < 4000 g parent subject 's legal representative speak understand Chinese Exclusion criterion ( formulafed group ) : fully partially breastfed infant infant breastfed > 20 % Exclusion criterion ( breastfed group ) : infant feed > 20 % infant formula Exclusion criterion ( infant ) : malformation , handicap congenital disease could affect normal feed growth treatment antibiotic
